happy-hacking-gnu

A free, open-source alternative to the HHKB Keymap Tool provided by PFU.

| Features                    | Supported | Planned |
|-----------------------------|:---------:|--------:|
| Remap individual keys       |  Yes      |  -      |
| Read keyboard information   |  Yes      |  -      |
| Reset factory defaults      |  Yes      |  -      |
| Dump firmware               |  Yes      |  -      |
| Update firmware             |  Yes      |  -      |

